            <noteGrp type="workDesc">
               <note type="description">Work ascribed to IA on the life and qualities of the
                     Prophet, including the palm-tree miracle in Seville. The text has been analysed
                     by Pablo Beneito (JMIAS 30, 2001).</note>
               <note type="structure"/>
